  "remarks": "TAi.073 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Deputy Minister of Haj and Religious Affairs under the Taliban regime b) Deputy Minister of Higher Education under the Taliban regime. Ethnic Pashtun from Baghlan Province. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Speaks fluent English, Urdu and Arabic. Afghan national identification card (tazkira) number 1136 issued. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 29 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 25 Jan. 2001 (amended on 3 Sep. 2003, 18 Jul. 2007, 21 Sep. 2007, 3 Oct. 2008, 29 Nov 2011 and 31 Dec. 2013)",
